### Navegación

#### Breadcrumbs
```css
.breadcrumb {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: var(--gray-500);
}

.breadcrumb-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.breadcrumb-item:not(:last-child)::after {
  content: '/';
  margin: 0 var(--space-2);
  color: var(--gray-400);
}

.breadcrumb-item a {
  color: var(--blue-500);
  text-decoration: none;
}

.breadcrumb-item a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}
```

