### Grid System
```css
.container {
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--space-4);
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .container { max-width: 640px; }
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .container { max-width: 768px; }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .container { max-width: 1024px; }
}

